{"tid":749284,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"河南加油站爆炸5傷　網傳顧客用手機掃碼釀禍","createTime":"2018-07-20T02:00:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-20T04:39:39.000Z","uid":39464,"like":48,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"60ef2a1df5cee8da212ba55be4afad16ac0578c3","tid":749284,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T02:00:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180719/photo/bkncn-20180719190342488-0719_05011_001_01p.jpg?20180719235030\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180719%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20180719190342488-0719_05011_001_01p.jpg%3F20180719235030&h=449b1b26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n河南濮陽縣一個路邊的加油站，周三（18日）下午4時30分左右突然發生爆炸，導致5人受傷、多車不同程度損壞。濮陽縣應急辦通報稱，傷者主要被燒傷或遭震碎的玻璃割傷，所幸經送院後均無生命危險。意外原因是施工導致天然氣管道破裂，氣體洩漏引發爆炸。 <br />\n<br />\n從網傳影片可見，爆炸發生後，油站被濃煙籠罩、周邊一片狼藉，大量雜物飛到旁邊的馬路路面，期間兩名赤裸上身的男傷者匆忙跑離現場。有知情者透露，爆炸是有民眾在加油站內，使用手機掃碼付款而引致，造成4人死亡。事發後，當地政府部門否認爆炸因手機掃碼付款引起。 <br />\n<br />\n據悉，由於高強度的手機信號，與加油站的電腦設備發生感應時，瞬間産生的電子摩擦有可能點燃汽油，故內地油站過往普遍禁止使用手機。但隨着行動支付日益流行，加上掃碼的感應時間較短、產生的電磁波功率較低，故許多油站已增設這種付款方式。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180719/bkncn-20180719190342488-0719_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180719%2Fbkncn-20180719190342488-0719_05011_001.html&d=KR2iNJyhpgUPMk8BaXJNfQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=65dcb636\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180719/bkncn-20180719190342488-0719_05011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"fe2deff3a7aea0b2dce72864d1170295ddb2e74e","tid":749284,"uid":126510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T02:03:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cdf8a4492d2a7db2cfe4f8d8e421b86f480e8f7","tid":749284,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T02:04:14.000Z","msg":"正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51d5f016f48134b14c5ef4d6e4fb3a83f091ae14","tid":749284,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T02:06:03.000Z","msg":"硬幣導致感應器的磁通量改變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6c27d63340eed06a24c90b470e3867a8bf121c4","tid":749284,"uid":123738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T02:06:34.000Z","msg":"無事無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n支那方式折「違規建築」啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b07f5a6840e69a921ead2166b353d28133b7bc9","tid":749284,"uid":141869,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T02:32:04.000Z","msg":"掃咩碼先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 用鏡頭影qr code根本唔會有咩電子摩擦，up得就up"},{"pid":"617c107641caa4fbd07a7fd132ef793b9c872db4","tid":749284,"uid":5891,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b07f5a6840e69a921ead2166b353d28133b7bc9","tid":749284,"uid":141869,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T02:32:04.000Z","msg":"掃咩碼先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 用鏡頭影qr code根本唔會有咩電子摩擦，up得就up"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T02:35:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 根本加油站就唔應該用手機"},{"pid":"de9bce9e608cc2aa09fca3e8f1872a56a5300595","tid":749284,"uid":8040,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5b07f5a6840e69a921e